review: Of course, the cheesecake at the Cheesecake Factory was quite yummy.  Even if you don't get a meal don't miss the desert :)  The food itself is quite innovative and diverse (Tex-Mex Egg rolls) which is one of the reasons that my wife and I have been eating at the place for years.  One appetizers that I dearly love is the Avocado Egg Roll.  Sounds weird I know but do try it out.  Finally, the service is consistently courteous and professional.  I definitely recommend the Cheesecake Factory.
